    dc:title "Microgomphus alani (Odonata, Gomphidae) sp. nov. from Cambodia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266820>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266817>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266818>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266821>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266822> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266820>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Idealised outlines of morphological details of the holotype (a-b, e-f) and paratype (c-d) of Microgomphus alani: a, c—hamuli, lateral view; b, d—hamuli, right hamuli, ventral view; e—anal appendages, dorsal view; f—head and thorax, lateral view; b—head and synthorax, frontal view; c—anal appendages, dorsal view; d—ditto, lateral view. Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/266820/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266817>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Microgomphus alani: general habitus of the holotype (a) and paratype (b) males and the wings of the holotype (c). Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/266817/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266818>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Morphological details of the holotype (a-f, h) and paratype (g) of Microgomphus alani: a—head and thorax, lateral view; b—head and synthorax, frontal view; c—anal appendages, dorsal view; d—ditto, lateral view; e—ditto, ventral view; fsecondary genitalia, lateral view; g—hamuli, lateral view; h—hamuli, ventral view. Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/266818/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266821>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Distal part (median and distal segments and posterior lobe) of the penis of the holotype of Microgomphus alani: a—lateral view; b—dorsolateral view; c—ventral view. Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/266821/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266822>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Habitats of Microgomphus alani: a—the type locality, Cambodia, Koh Kong Province, 17 km ENE of Koh Kong, ‘ Macromia Rivulet’, 11 ° 40 ' 17 '' N, 103 ° 07 ' 28 '' E, 296 m a. s. l., 3 vi 2014; b—the habitat of the paratype, Cambodia, Koh Kong Province, 6.5 km SW Thma Bang village, the ‘ Microgomphus River’, the slow reach upstream the bridge, 15 iv 2010." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/266822/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

